title: Hidden Dragon Legend-CODEX RePack
description:
Title: Hidden Dragon: Legend
Genre: Violent, Gore, Action, Indie
Developer: MegaFun Games Ltd.
Publisher: Oasis Games
Release Date: Jan 22, 2018

RePack Info:

Nothing was removed, game archives unpacked for better ratio.
Strong compression using precomp, srep and arc.
Decompression should take ~10min on a decent machine.

Installation:

1. Mount the .ISO image using daemon tools or unpack it using winrar.

4. Enjoy & Seed ;)
